#
#  PGML 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

A plane starts from rest and travels in a straight line motion as shown by the graph below. Create an [`a - s`] graph and find the values of acceleration
at [`s = [$A], [$B]`] and [`[$C]`] [`s`] to three decimal points. 


[`a_{[$A]} =`] [_____]{"$s1"} [`m/s^2`]  
[`a_{[$B]} =`] [_____]{"$s2"} [`m/s^2`]  
[`a_{[$C]} =`] [_____]{"$s3"} [`m/s^2`]  


